8.012  Pro ject  Proposal:  The  8.012  Pro ject  is  a  design-your-own  pro ject  to  explore  some  of 
the  concepts  we’ve  been  learning  in  class.  It  is  free-form  in  the  sense  you  can  design  any  kind 
of  (reasonable)  pro ject  you  can  think  of  related  to  the  class,  but  in  the  spirit  of  Newton  should 
nevertheless be experimental  in design.  The pro ject  itself will be due on Wednesday,  November 
26th  in  your  recitation  section,  and  is  worth  5%  of  your  total  grade. 

Here  are  the  ground  rules  for  the  8.012  pro ject  (see  also  the  8.012  webpage): 

